                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/686" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0087</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9491 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云内动力内幕交易及经营状况透视</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Analysis on Insider trading and operating conditions of perspective</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张继德</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">昆明云内动力股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内幕交易；云内动力；资本市场；注册会计师；证监会</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Insider trading；Cloud inside dynamic；Capital market；Certified public accountants；CSRC</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010年11月19日，中国证监会表示，中国首例注册会计师利用内幕信息违规交易股票案被查实，目前仍有多位涉嫌违规的注册会计师在被调查中，证监会还通报了5家证券投资咨询机构违规行为。这标志着证监会查处涉嫌内幕交易案件涉案人员，开始向更加多元化的方向发展，同时也显示，证监会的查处手段更加多样。2010年4月20日云内动力公告称，公司于近日接到深圳证券交易所《关于对昆明云内动力股份有限公司的年报问询函》，发现该公司《2010年年度报告》中未对《公司内幕信息知情人登记制度》的执行情况进行披露，于是公司按相关要求补充公告《公司内幕信息知情人登记制度》的执行情况。很遗憾，补充公告的结果竟然显示该公司2009年年报签字会计师，以及公司高管的直系亲属均存在内幕交易行为。除此之外，年报数据同时显示，公司营业利润及现金等纷纷出现负数，有业内人士认为，从这些信息来看，云内动力的主营持续盈利能力有待考量。近日，昆明市国资委与中国兵装集团就云南内燃机厂与兵装集团产权合作事宜达成协议，昆明市国资委拟将所持有的云南内燃机厂100%的产权无偿划转给兵装集团全资子公司中国长安。国有产权转让，中国长安向云内动力利益输送的资产是优良资产还是非优良资产现不知道，所以国有产权转让会给云内动力带来生机还是给投资者画了一张饼不好讲。本案例旨在使学生对上市公司内幕交易的特征以及对内幕交易的防范和治理有更深层次的认识，并提高学生进行财务报表分析和对公司前景分析的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On November 19，2010，the China securities regulatory commission officials said China&#39;s first registered accountant with inside information illegal trading stock case was thorough check，still have several suspected illegal certified public accountants are investigated，it also reported five securities investment consulting agency irregularities. This marks the CSRC investigate alleged insider trading case allowing researchers began to more diversified direction，it also showed that，the CSRC investigation means more varied. On April 20，2010，says cloud inside dynamic announcement in recently received the shenzhen stock exchange on the inside dynamic in kunming cloud of a joint stock limited company annals of inquiry letter， it is found that the company&#39;s &quot;2010 of the annual report of the company not insider information insider registration system&quot; of implementation，so the company disclosed according to the relevant requirements supplement the announcement &quot;company insider information insider registration system of implementation. Unfortunately， supplement the announcement of the result unexpectedly shows that the company is 2009 annual report，and signed by the certified public accountants executives there are immediate family insider trading behavior. In addition，annual data shows at the same time，the company operating profit and cash to wait have been shown negative，the personage inside course of study thinks， judging from the information within the main motivation，the clouds to sustained profitability considerations. Recently，kunming with Chinese soldiers SASAC installed group with soldiers loaded the yunnan internal combustion engine group property cooperation agreement，kunming will be proposed to the sasac held by the property of yunnan internal-combustion factory 100% free transfer to soldier pack wholly-owned subsidiaries China enterprise group. The transfer of the state-owned property right，China enterprise interior impetus to cloud the assets are conveying interests fine assets or blame fine assets now don&#39;t know，so the transfer of the state-owned property right will give cloud inside dynamic with life still give investors drew a bread hard to say. This case in order to make students of the listed company，the characteristics and insider trading on insider trading prevention and management have deeper understanding，and improve students&#39; financial statement analysis and prospect of company analysis skills.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《财务报表分析》、《企业战略》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">美国内幕交易归责理论；平等享有信息理论；受托义务理论；非法挪用理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
